    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but the \"rest\" you're talking about... it's just more of the same. more waking up in a body that feels like it doesn't belong to me. if the person who actually lived is already gone, then what's actually left? it feels like I'm just a burden to everyone by dragging this nothingness around. wouldn't it be more peaceful if the shell just stopped existing?",
